#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.90"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.90:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.90:0.2"
msgid "9. Theravagga "
msgstr "9. Senior Mendicants "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.90:0.3"
msgid "90. Khīṇāsavabalasutta "
msgstr "90. The Powers of One Who has Ended Defilements "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.90:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Sāriputta went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.90:1.2"
msgid "“kati nu kho, sāriputta, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno balāni, yehi balehi samannāgato khīṇāsavo bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayaṃ paṭijānāti: "
msgstr "“Sāriputta, how many powers does a mendicant who has ended the defilements have that qualify them to claim: "

msgctxt "an10.90:1.3"
msgid "‘khīṇā me āsavā’”ti? "
msgstr "‘My defilements have ended.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.175, sc2
msgctxt "an10.90:2.1"
msgid "“Dasa, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno balāni, yehi balehi samannāgato khīṇāsavo bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayaṃ paṭijānāti: "
msgstr "“Sir, a mendicant who has ended the defilements has ten powers that qualify them to claim: "

msgctxt "an10.90:2.2"
msgid "‘khīṇā me āsavā’ti. "
msgstr "‘My defilements have ended.’ "

msgctxt "an10.90:2.3"
msgid "Katamāni dasa? "
msgstr "What ten? "

msgctxt "an10.90:2.4"
msgid "Idha, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno aniccato sabbe saṅkhārā yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhā honti. "
msgstr "Firstly, a mendicant with defilements ended has clearly seen with right wisdom all conditions as truly impermanent. "

msgctxt "an10.90:2.5"
msgid "Yampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno aniccato sabbe saṅkhārā yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhā honti, idampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno balaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ āgamma khīṇāsavo bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayaṃ paṭijānāti: "
msgstr "This is a power that a mendicant who has ended the defilements relies on to claim: "

msgctxt "an10.90:2.6"
msgid "‘khīṇā me āsavā’ti. (1) "
msgstr "‘My defilements have ended.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.90:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno aṅgārakāsūpamā kāmā yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhā honti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant with defilements ended has clearly seen with right wisdom that sensual pleasures are truly like a pit of glowing coals. "

msgctxt "an10.90:3.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno aṅgārakāsūpamā kāmā yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhā honti, idampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno balaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ āgamma khīṇāsavo bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayaṃ paṭijānāti: "
msgstr "This is a power that a mendicant who has ended the defilements relies on to claim: "

msgctxt "an10.90:3.3"
msgid "‘khīṇā me āsavā’ti. (2) "
msgstr "‘My defilements have ended.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.90:4.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno vivekaninnaṃ cittaṃ hoti vivekapoṇaṃ vivekapabbhāraṃ vivekaṭṭhaṃ nekkhammābhirataṃ byantībhūtaṃ sabbaso āsavaṭṭhāniyehi dhammehi. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the mind of a mendicant with defilements ended slants, slopes, and inclines to seclusion. They’re withdrawn, loving renunciation, and they’ve totally done with defiling influences. "

msgctxt "an10.90:4.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno vivekaninnaṃ cittaṃ hoti vivekapoṇaṃ vivekapabbhāraṃ vivekaṭṭhaṃ nekkhammābhirataṃ byantībhūtaṃ sabbaso āsavaṭṭhāniyehi dhammehi, idampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno balaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ āgamma khīṇāsavo bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayaṃ paṭijānāti: "
msgstr "This is a power that a mendicant who has ended the defilements relies on to claim: "

msgctxt "an10.90:4.3"
msgid "‘khīṇā me āsavā’ti. (3) "
msgstr "‘My defilements have ended.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an10.90:5.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvitā honti subhāvitā. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant with defilements ended has well developed the four kinds of mindfulness meditation. "

msgctxt "an10.90:5.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvitā honti subhāvitā, idampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno balaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ āgamma khīṇāsavo bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayaṃ paṭijānāti: "
msgstr "This is a power that a mendicant who has ended the defilements relies on to claim: "

msgctxt "an10.90:5.3"
msgid "‘khīṇā me āsavā’ti. (4) "
msgstr "‘My defilements have ended.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.176, sc6
msgctxt "an10.90:6.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno cattāro sammappadhānā bhāvitā honti subhāvitā … pe … "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant with defilements ended has well developed the four right efforts. … "

msgctxt "an10.90:6.2"
msgid "cattāro iddhipādā bhāvitā honti subhāvitā … pe … "
msgstr "the four bases of psychic power … "

msgctxt "an10.90:6.3"
msgid "pañcindriyāni … "
msgstr "the five faculties … "

msgctxt "an10.90:6.4"
msgid "pañca balāni bhāvitāni honti subhāvitāni … "
msgstr "the five powers … "

msgctxt "an10.90:6.5"
msgid "satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā honti subhāvitā … "
msgstr "the seven awakening factors … "

msgctxt "an10.90:6.6"
msgid "ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvito hoti subhāvito. "
msgstr "the noble eightfold path. "

msgctxt "an10.90:6.7"
msgid "Yampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvito hoti subhāvito, idampi, bhante, khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno balaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ āgamma khīṇāsavo bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayaṃ paṭijānāti: "
msgstr "This is a power that a mendicant who has ended the defilements relies on to claim: "

msgctxt "an10.90:6.8"
msgid "‘khīṇā me āsavā’ti. (5–10.) "
msgstr "‘My defilements have ended.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an10.90:7.1"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhante, dasa khīṇāsavassa bhikkhuno balāni, yehi balehi samannāgato khīṇāsavo bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayaṃ paṭijānāti: "
msgstr "A mendicant who has ended the defilements has these ten powers that qualify them to claim: "

msgctxt "an10.90:7.2"
msgid "‘khīṇā me āsavā’”ti. "
msgstr "‘My defilements have ended.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.90:7.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.90:7.4"
msgid "Theravaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an10.90:8.1"
msgid "Vāhanānando puṇṇiyo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an10.90:8.2"
msgid "byākaraṃ katthimāniko; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an10.90:8.3"
msgid "Napiyakkosakokāli, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an10.90:8.4"
msgid "khīṇāsavabalena cāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
